text:
Chiyuki-san,
Is there anything left to hang?

No, it's all done already.
It's quicker when we do it together.

Chiyuki-san, you're so efficient,
I ended up making you work twice as hard.

At least let me handle
bringing in the laundry by myself...!

No,
you don't have to worry about that.

Somehow... even though it's called a training camp,
it doesn't feel much different from our usual dorm life.
The tension, in a good way, isn't there.

But── seeing Juri-chan in her lesson mode like this
isn't something I get to see often.
For me, it's still a valuable experience...

When I see Juri-chan's serious expression,
it makes me want to work harder too!

Uh...
Just hearing that made me feel suddenly tense.

I'm sorry, I didn't mean it like that...
Everything's fine, just like usual, right?
